channel.title: Cody's Webclient Tool [BETA]
channel.description:
Welcome, i was bored and i wrote a webclient tool. Virus scan says there's 1 virus, it's a false positive, if you dont TRUST ME sandboxie it. ~THIS MIGHT NOT WORK FOR WIN7 USER'S IF YOU RECIEVE AN ERROR WHILE OPENING THE BUILDER PLEASE POST HERE, I WILL RE-FORMAT IT FOR WIN7~
[b]To use this tool you will need:[/b] A Webclient A Server Name A Brain
[b]Download:[/b] http://www.mediafire.com/?p727bn64gp5cb60
[b]Step 1:[/b] Open up the builder, not the stub! and enter your Server Name and webclient link then click on "build" (I'll use runescape for this) [IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/mt3uc9.jpg[/img]
[b]Step 2:[/b] A server.exe should appear in your folder directory (the folder the stub and builder are in) click on that [IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/96b3f9.jpg[/img] That should popup, as you can see theres your server name on the top and on the bottom of the program! There's an auto typer, and an auto clicker. Go down to "open webclient" and it should open you're webclient, use the tool's (auto typer) (auto clicker) to help you in the game! Owner's may use this to release there client's for small download's.
Please leave feedback enjoy!
